node.text:
We sat down with our founder & formulator to chat all things immunity & how the key is getting as many herbs, spices and adaptogens into your routine as possible. 
Want to learn more? Leave questions in the comments below!

node.accessibility_caption: Photo shared by Goldthread Plant-Based Tonics on August 13, 2021 tagging @hannahrose2k__. May be an image of bottle and outdoors.

node.text:
Hello weekend, we see you. ☀️🌊⁠
Mint Condition + a cruise to the beach is our favorite way to relax after a long week. What's yours?⁠
#DrinkMorePlants (📷: @hannahrose2k__)

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Goldthread Plant-Based Tonics on August 12, 2021. May be an image of drink and indoor.

node.text:
Each of our tonics was created with feeling and function in mind! ⁠
🍵 Looking for some energy? Grab Japanese Matcha. ⁠
🍇 Want to boost your immunity? Elderberry Defense is your jam. ⁠
🌞 Need to activate digestion? Turmeric Radiance is there for you.  Learn more about the rest of our lineup via our link in bio. ⁠
#DrinkMorePlants

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Goldthread Plant-Based Tonics on August 11, 2021. May be an image of outdoors.

node.text:
FROM FARM TO BOTTLE 🌎⁠
Our founder & formulator @williamsiff travels all over the world to develop long-term, mutually beneficial relationships with the farmers supplying our herbs, spices, and adaptogens. #DrinkMorePlants every day to support our incredible growers. ✨🌿⁠

node.accessibility_caption: Photo shared by Goldthread Plant-Based Tonics on August 09, 2021 tagging @johnedwardsmarket. May be an image of drink.

node.text: Looking for Goldthread? 👀 🌿 Our store locator makes it easier than ever to find Goldthread in a store near you. #DrinkMorePlants (📷: @johnedwardsmarket )

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Goldthread Plant-Based Tonics on August 06, 2021. May be an image of one or more people, nature and tree.

node.text:
The best weekends are spent in nature. ⛰️🌞 ⁠
Where are you exploring this weekend? ⁠
Comment below 👇⁠

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Goldthread Plant-Based Tonics on August 05, 2021. May be an image of pool and text that says 'Which Goldthread tonic is best for relaxation?'.

node.text:
Our go-to tonics for relaxation:⁣⁠
Lavender Bliss: hand-picked lavender from the Rhone Valley in France meets a blend of teas and herbs for a soothing wave of natural calm.⁣ ⁠
Mint Condition: mountain tea and mint from the hills of Greece refreshes and soothes with fresh-squeezed lemon for a refreshing end to any stressful day.⁣ ⁠
Tap our #linkinbio to learn more!⁣ 💜🌱⁠
#DrinkMorePlants ⁣⁠

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Goldthread Plant-Based Tonics on August 03, 2021. May be an image of drink.

node.text: Mint Condition 🌱 Inspired by the beautiful Greek islands, the cool, crisp and refreshing plants in Mint Condition are full of antioxidants and phytonutrients which help improve and support overall vibrant health and longevity. Mint has long been used throughout various cultures as a reliable way to improve digestive health and create feelings of wellbeing. #DrinkMorePlants

node.text:
Mint Mocktail ✔️✔️✔️ made by our friend Salia @holisticcocktails! Check out the recipe below & give it a try! ⁣
⁣
🌱 Combine 1 oz cucumber, 1 oz @seedlipdrinks Grove 42 and 1/3 oz @herbpharm Lavender Anxiety Soother in glass & muddle. ⁣
💃 Add ice and shake. ⁣
🧊 Pour over ice in new glass. ⁣
🥄 Top with Mint Condition & stir. ⁣
🍋 Add lime and rosemary for garnish & enjoy! ⁣
⁣
(📸: @holisticcocktails) ⁣
